Name: In-N-Out
Description: Songs with cool intros and/or outros.

Name: Rhythm Section Want Ad
Description: The percussion in this song is done by drum machine(s), not by drum human(s).

Name: Nobel in Literature
Description: Bare your soul by submitting a song where you think the lyrics are fantastic poetry. For everyone's ease in judging, song submissions are ONLY IN ENGLISH.

Name: Avoid Certain Death
Description: The scenario: you've magnanimously agreed to drive Shauna to the airport at 4 am. You need music to stay awake, but if you play anything that causes Shauna to have a conniption because it's "too early for that" you might die in a different way. So you need to pick a soothing, yet interesting song.

Name: Zoomies
Description: This song can be anything with a fast tempo! BPM cutoff left to your personal judgment.

Name: Bird is the Word
Description: This song mentions birds, either a particular kind of bird, birds in general, or a reference to flying, soaring, eggs, or feathers.
